{"tid":1935510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無諗過香港連悼念都要流水式","createTime":"2020-03-20T15:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T13:05:52.000Z","uid":171627,"like":125,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"be283860e8cc2fc547f5774c612b0bcd41fe72f5","tid":1935510,"uid":171627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:18:37.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac出，講大話死全家，一世嫁唔出<br />\n大家有仼何意見請留言賜教 唔關ac主人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為確保22號會去悼念嘅手足安全，請幫忙推到佢哋都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">無諗過香港會連一個悼念都容不下<br />\n無懼白色恐怖 流水式悼念<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n仲要小心肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(&acute;･_･`)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3月22日 彥霖6個月流水式悼念會</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHdeP8X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHdeP8X.png&h=4dcfef95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[3/20最新update:保持馬路範圍暢通，鮮花區已移到最右，下面有詳細圖作參考，sorly<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">好多人都話尚十玩爛哂<br />\n但有冇諗過人係生嘅 地係死嘅<br />\n人唔識走 悼念地方轉哂十八區都唔會安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果連悼念都做到be water，唔聚集，企疏啲<br />\n就可以大大減低被捕率<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲可以小心肺炎</span><br />\n<br />\n大家都仲記得<br />\n2月8日，黑警點樣喺將軍澳入屋苑濫捕<br />\n3月8日，黑警點樣喺祭壇拉封鎖線全人類SS<br />\n<br />\n1. 拉既主要都係街坊和理非，仲要唔係black bloc <br />\n2. 兩次都好多街坊或者手足停留圍觀無離開<br />\n<br />\n就講3月8日<br />\n吸取過以往經驗，現場不停有手足大嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「手足企疏啲！」<br />\n「留返條通道丫唔該哂」<br />\n「手足擺完蠟燭麻煩企前少少啦」<br />\n但奈何大家唔知邊條先係通道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好自然企疏3秒又企返密<br />\n手足又有好多野想同梓樂講<br />\n擺蠟燭條隊好自然長到轉哂彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">將軍澳手足今次想試行流水式悼念<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如下: </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUeQ72L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUeQ72L.png&h=07f888df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">絲我唔係好識比例，sorly，放心到時會有清晰膠紙係地下提大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 手足放好蠟燭默哀完成後請稍移玉步可以行前少少換個地方繼續悼念，比更多手足機會參與，同埋小心肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 雖然走唔走自己決定，但不被捕不受傷一直係大家既宗旨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 祭壇將設有鮮花區及2個蠟燭區<br />\n4. 地面會有白膠紙作簡單指示，請順住箭咀方向擺放蠟燭及鮮花<br />\n5. 蠟燭請放喺白線範圍內，上次大家既心意太多越放越出，差唔多佔半條道路，走既時候好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6. 綠色範圍係行人路，好歡迎記者拍攝FA stand by，但我哋一齊保持通道暢通，企疏啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果手足想悼念/等人/休息，建議行前少少，唔好停喺行人路怕大家人來人往撞親你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7. 二樓我會放多少少關於交通既資料<br />\n8. 戴好口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小心肺炎，避免人群聚集<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\np.s.<br />\n我唔係大台/host，亦唔會去干涉每位手足既行動<br />\n只可以諗啲方法等大家安全少少咁進行悼念<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但當然天氣，人數，手足反應，路況，我地都控制唔到，只可以係配置準備方面做好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尚十壇從來唔係屬於仼何一個人，呢個同梓樂彥霖之間既連繫，從來都屬於所有手足，多謝每位為祭壇付出過嘅你哋。<br />\n<br />\n特別多謝: <br />\n各位手足，將軍澳烽火台，香港人抗爭日程表文宣頻道出，人流管理經驗人士<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命 </span></span>"},{"pid":"982e443490a480cc5bf2aa66f32d407ca78d717c","tid":1935510,"uid":171627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"留個二樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />mine"},{"pid":"b0654bb043e4d9bf32e079541cb7464cd9659acb","tid":1935510,"uid":345002,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">藍絲一早出左張POSTER話打曱甴, 然後元朗唔關站,<br />\n原因係:<br />\n1. <ins>嚇和理非,唔敢出黎</ins><br />\n2. <ins>等勇武帶工具&quot;覆桌&quot; 原來係假既, 再大圍捕 &amp; SS 一獲拉晒</ins><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第2點,第2點,第2點<br />\n好重要, 好重要, 好重要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今次一定大班記者在場<br />\n我唔係好信再有721發生, 上次都未搞掂, 又黎一次, 班Popo死緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><br />\n721靜坐, 請唔好帶任何文具,<br />\n101% 逐個Check 唔好比Popo有藉口入拉你<br />\n<br />\n<ins>**建議只帶 背囊(放本書), 正常長遮/縮骨遮 (可能落雨),口罩,文宣,手機**</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*****唔該廣傳比各位手足*****</span></span>"},{"pid":"ceca45e8cb66fc5657521ede20c4b689ab66edce","tid":1935510,"uid":235319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:25:20.000Z","msg":"推推推 手足唔係condom, 永遠唔會忘記!"},{"pid":"cdc2a5aaf7d4407236e9163b7dacc2fea37dc91a","tid":1935510,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"手足唔喺condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c921b21dbd8168d4c2373e1204938ae46154d6e","tid":1935510,"uid":310474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d6ef7de27b95830e5d0c36ffd3f7e6544ee6bf","tid":1935510,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b4f7497915687ed25069711f78c2e6071376d158","tid":1935510,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"d6abfa58c1939cf7a4f65ff73ef5b9f6710fa664","tid":1935510,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"一齊行埋手足個份！"},{"pid":"2f1f6044b3b65c8abaf74b8c8cb927e8433b619b","tid":1935510,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"帶埋佢地煲底見"},{"pid":"2fd3b0bd51d3b5e054caca686d484d82b52f3bbb","tid":1935510,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:28:54.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"2085d9a840e1f95c8706707665f8fe182574fdd3","tid":1935510,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"多謝手足為悼念絞盡腦汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8147c69e6618cb7e4d1298d89382e33bf6a671e0","tid":1935510,"uid":225100,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"今日割五城<br />\n明日割十城"},{"pid":"e477fb20cba930ff7d36cfb9aac347678cb1750d","tid":1935510,"uid":104917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"執生"},{"pid":"e95ce73f51184a9dac40e4f97741d7915b04fe05","tid":1935510,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:32:00.000Z","msg":"全民做哨"},{"pid":"b59dff2d28b4f53228335922f4167e6f4cc57028","tid":1935510,"uid":172465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d956c839df2c55118fd870e7a86a749866a7c56","tid":1935510,"uid":175731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:45:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4040c755f9a47808aa068f448698dbbcc6c4e20c","tid":1935510,"uid":72334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:46:25.000Z","msg":"出去嘅麻煩大家做定48小時心理準備<br />\n另外上次濫捕嘅手足告鳩班狗未"},{"pid":"2f1eb65c458c1748ef17a7af01753527e699f12f","tid":1935510,"uid":61002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"喺停車場入邊排隊會唔會好啲，由上層排返落地下拜祭"},{"pid":"cd351d8d3c0572c7c5262453b9084bde652d6b00","tid":1935510,"uid":256671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心肺炎 小心黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be435d4e2d9002d0fab9f1d4b46fa8911bcf79b","tid":1935510,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:52:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a45ffc8aa2f9ab3a86172279c992418b9a8c340b","tid":1935510,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"送頭行動，心中記念就夠啦"},{"pid":"8c6514890b8fc2e41683a13f1068193201b07718","tid":1935510,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:53:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"620aafbb9c87a769e85e901b88b533961bdf1518","tid":1935510,"uid":19664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6b212e5bf113cac980d29a00e5b92837ba37a3","tid":1935510,"uid":76365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"Thx OP"},{"pid":"ab82bb8142f0352ddb61f6e5e398b1bfd3f95aa5","tid":1935510,"uid":19664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e66ebc4e056789d4c5792d82f22d4d8bfa3161","tid":1935510,"uid":19664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17873c047b50b93b50808d2d621e360ad59534e3","tid":1935510,"uid":19664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ce7252844a591cebd1afc066265c39e7bcb2ba","tid":1935510,"uid":324229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"突發 自撚私留學生剪手帶 違反隔離令 開左ig page 幫手share<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1935426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1935426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c54468886759e9e0392a443fb0cab30275144b66","tid":1935510,"uid":171627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f1eb65c458c1748ef17a7af01753527e699f12f","tid":1935510,"uid":61002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"喺停車場入邊排隊會唔會好啲，由上層排返落地下拜祭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"感謝ching意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都有諗過呢個問題<br />\n如果觀濱，di，尚十 3個地方平分人流之後都多人<br />\n有一定人數會考慮叫手足一齊係旁邊棵樹既停車場門排上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335a92970d86f4060f156c30b75ed188d03d2005","tid":1935510,"uid":171627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b59dff2d28b4f53228335922f4167e6f4cc57028","tid":1935510,"uid":172465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"希望可以同各位手足一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89b83cc6347adad53c39fbfd9e1e3952c4dd96f","tid":1935510,"uid":3406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fc17828d457d1b4d3a5336f27c5ecaf21612be","tid":1935510,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b87081d063d3be1d4de09e4301e55869d7faff8c","tid":1935510,"uid":171627,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dUE9EBp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdUE9EBp.png&h=76b7fb1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講多少少交通同埋路線先<br />\n張圖有 <span style=\"color: violet;\">上</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">下</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">左 </span><span style=\"color: blue;\">右</span>4個方向<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上: 除左撞牆之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實兩邊有門可以行樓梯上停車場，但停車場成日有狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔建議上，一定要上嘅千其唔好落單，大家都記得梓樂事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">下: 呢條係去popcorn，富康花園，黨鐵既直接馬路，好多時狗都會拎呢條馬路先，之後先再拎巴士總站個條，如果被block就用巴士總站個條，或者去面向祭壇既<span style=\"color: blue;\">右邊會有天橋</span>可去富康(記得睇下哨gp狗有冇拎左富康橋)</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">左: 呢條馬路可以去巴士總站，多數呢條無左，即係<span style=\"color: gold;\">下面既popcorn富康馬路</span>都封左，咁可以經廣明再兜巴士總站</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">右: 可以上富康橋(同上，睇清楚有無狗，勿落單)，可以去尙德另一個出口，可以行隧道，但個人唔建議行，同埋尚德另一個出口係泊狗車既熱門地，人流唔算多，真係要行都唔好落單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">巴士總站:</span><br />\n<br />\n巴士會因應情況停駛既，狗有無攞馬路都係重點，但如果大家真係有流水式不逗留，照計應該坐巴士走到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n296A: 尚德to 牛頭角站(循環線)，途經創紀之城、觀塘市中心及觀塘游泳池<br />\n<br />\n296C: 尚德to 長沙灣(海盈邨)，途經觀塘市中心、牛頭角下邨、九龍灣德福花園、新蒲崗太子道東、九龍城亞皆老街、旺角彌敦道及深水埗長沙灣道 / 荔枝角道<br />\n<br />\n296P: 尚德to 旺角，指定時間先有車，個人覺得搭296C實際啲<br />\n<br />\n296D: 尚德to 九龍站，途經觀塘繞道、啟德隧道、紅磡（祇限回程)、佐敦、尖沙咀和環球貿易廣場。佢等車20分鐘鬆d先一班，但勝在少站夠快<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">再次建議手足揾定離開路線，尤其外區手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁就唔洗大家一齊企係度慢慢search，小心肺炎喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"4da4dbf00bb3fcf2d872ced26369bf20e7879cdf","tid":1935510,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f7497915687ed25069711f78c2e6071376d158","tid":1935510,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:28:14.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989d79be6e78f67ac1938638d558ca0f516ed754","tid":1935510,"uid":292151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔應該set死個時間 係有心嘅，喺22號任何時間都可以送花 <br />\n<br />\n想個畫面好睇啲但係一大堆人被捕 定冇咁好睇，代價係不受傷不被捕？"},{"pid":"ff74ac3bd268ff2d1cbf166fc968ba1430b27950","tid":1935510,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a635c902c6fb6eb7991ca563cd9f3623dd8c2bd5","tid":1935510,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0654bb043e4d9bf32e079541cb7464cd9659acb","tid":1935510,"uid":345002,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">藍絲一早出左張POSTER話打曱甴, 然後元朗唔關站,<br />\n原因係:<br />\n1. <ins>嚇和理非,唔敢出黎</ins><br />\n2. <ins>等勇武帶工具&quot;覆桌&quot; 原來係假既, 再大圍捕 &amp; SS 一獲拉晒</ins><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第2點,第2點,第2點<br />\n好重要, 好重要, 好重要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今次一定大班記者在場<br />\n我唔係好信再有721發生, 上次都未搞掂, 又黎一次, 班Popo死緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><br />\n721靜坐, 請唔好帶任何文具,<br />\n101% 逐個Check 唔好比Popo有藉口入拉你<br />\n<br />\n<ins>**建議只帶 背囊(放本書), 正常長遮/縮骨遮 (可能落雨),口罩,文宣,手機**</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*****唔該廣傳比各位手足*****</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:52:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9034f9c2913234bcc9d09f273e08c3864c58f60f","tid":1935510,"uid":271690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:03:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ef282333e1e62a04e5d04f4943fa4cf60fab452","tid":1935510,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:07:18.000Z","msg":"除左楊明仲有呢班藝人唔好漏左佢地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1935695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1935695</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"99d1a596333eebd5b7b75366550f2c26907daf56","tid":1935510,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c54468886759e9e0392a443fb0cab30275144b66","tid":1935510,"uid":171627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f1eb65c458c1748ef17a7af01753527e699f12f","tid":1935510,"uid":61002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"喺停車場入邊排隊會唔會好啲，由上層排返落地下拜祭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:57:30.000Z","msg":"感謝ching意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都有諗過呢個問題<br />\n如果觀濱，di，尚十 3個地方平分人流之後都多人<br />\n有一定人數會考慮叫手足一齊係旁邊棵樹既停車場門排上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T18:26:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">上次都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該都係咁上下最多<br />\n好似marco生忌咁上下都係</span>"},{"pid":"8764754dc0a451c87cf365b9badaf8679f46bece","tid":1935510,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d1a596333eebd5b7b75366550f2c26907daf56","tid":1935510,"uid":61002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c54468886759e9e0392a443fb0cab30275144b66","tid":1935510,"uid":171627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score